Package com.ibm.watson.speech_to_text.v1.model

Interface ListAcousticModelsOptions.Language

Enclosing class:
ListAcousticModelsOptions
public static interface ListAcousticModelsOptions.Language
The identifier of the language for which custom language or custom acoustic models are to be returned. Omit the parameter to see all custom language or custom acoustic models that are owned by the requesting credentials. (**Note:** The identifier `ar-AR` is deprecated; use `ar-MS` instead.)

To determine the languages for which customization is available, see [Language support for customization](https://cloud.ibm.com/docs/speech-to-text?topic=speech-to-text-customization#languageSupport).
